{"TopicId":70991,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"I built a successful VTOL!","CreatedByName":"neamerjell","CreatedById":86054,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-30T00:34:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"neamerjell","CreatedById":86054,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-30T00:34:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ve been trying to make a VTOL with no wings, basically a helicopter with jet engines instead of rotors. Here is what I came up with...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERequired Parts:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EB9 Aerospace\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELack Luster Labs\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMechjeb (deleted the parts, kept the .dlls and .cfgs)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMechJebandRemtoteTechforAll.cfg \u003Ca href=\u0022http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/mechjeb-and-remotetech-for-all/http://\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://kerbalspaceprogram.com/mechjeb-and-remotetech-for-all/http://\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E^^^ this adds Mechjeb to all command modules and pods\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECraft File: \u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.neamerjell.com/projects/ksp/Dragonfly.craft\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.neamerjell.com/projects/ksp/Dragonfly.craft\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe thrust of the engines is reduced to about 50%, which was more than enough to put it on the helipad.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI added the airbrakes so that I could kill rotational and lateral motion more quickly without having to angle the engines and have to fiddle with the throttle just to get back to something resembling a hover. All the airbrakes are keyed to a single action group.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.neamerjell.com/projects/ksp/dragonfly1.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022dragonfly1.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.neamerjell.com/projects/ksp/dragonfly2.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022dragonfly2.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.neamerjell.com/projects/ksp/dragonfly3.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022dragonfly3.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.neamerjell.com/projects/ksp/dragonfly4.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022dragonfly4.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-04-30T00:37:30Z\u0022 title=\u002204/30/2014 12:37  AM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EApril 30, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by neamerjell\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Voculus","CreatedById":85437,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-30T01:15:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENice craft! Hugely satisfying, isn\u0027t it? Building and flying VTOLs is one of the most difficult, but rewarding experiences in the game. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"lionblaze63","CreatedById":100767,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-30T01:27:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ecan you give links to the mods you used?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"neamerjell","CreatedById":86054,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-30T14:19:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022lionblaze63\u0022 data-cite=\u0022lionblaze63\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003Ecan you give links to the mods you used?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMechJeb: \u003Ca href=\u0022http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/mechjeb/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://kerbalspaceprogram.com/mechjeb/\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EMechJeb and Remote Tech for All : \u003Ca href=\u0022http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/mechjeb-and-remotetech-for-all/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://kerbalspaceprogram.com/mechjeb-and-remotetech-for-all/\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELack Luster Labs: \u003Ca href=\u0022http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/lacklusterlabs/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://kerbalspaceprogram.com/lacklusterlabs/\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EB9 Aerospace: \u003Ca href=\u0022http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/0-20-2-b9-aerospace-pack-r3-1/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://kerbalspaceprogram.com/0-20-2-b9-aerospace-pack-r3-1/\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ETo get B9 to work with 23.5: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/8bjgxv65yshg2z3/B9%20KSP%200.23.5.zip\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/8bjgxv65yshg2z3/B9%20KSP%200.23.5.zip\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI think that\u0027s all that is required for the craft. I actually found some updates to my mods while digging up these links. Thanks for making me do that \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOh, and if you want my NavBall:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENavball Texture Export: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://bitbucket.org/xEvilReeperx/ksp_navballtexturechanger/downloads/KSP-0.23.5-NavBallChanger-v1.2.zip\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://bitbucket.org/xEvilReeperx/ksp_navballtexturechanger/downloads/KSP-0.23.5-NavBallChanger-v1.2.zip\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe texture image I use: \u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.neamerjell.com/projects/ksp/navball.png\u0022 alt=\u0022navball.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-04-30T14:34:36Z\u0022 title=\u002204/30/2014 02:34  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EApril 30, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by neamerjell\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"neamerjell","CreatedById":86054,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-30T21:18:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Voculus\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Voculus\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ENice craft! Hugely satisfying, isn\u0027t it? Building and flying VTOLs is one of the most difficult, but rewarding experiences in the game. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThanks. Hugely satisfying? Definitely! One of the most difficult things to do? That\u0027s debatable. For me, it became easy after seeing a few tutorial videos:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/13XSzUogxo8?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/iMi77hLvROw?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/StyQxiN1OkI?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003EOnce I learned to balance the craft and limit the max thrust on the engines, the rest came easy with some trial and crashing. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"How2FoldSoup","CreatedById":82003,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-30T21:28:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThat LLL cockpit is amazing...Thank you for sharing this because I\u0027ve got ideas for designs with it now \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}